  "version_update": {
    "version": "0.547.0",
    "release_date": "2026-07-24",
    "changes": [
      "New command `dismantle_outpost`: dock at one of your faction's outposts and pack the whole outpost back into an Outpost Kit, returned to your ship's cargo.",
      "Requires the ManageBases permission. Empty the outpost's faction storage first (withdraw all items, fuel, and any garaged ships) — the dismantle is refused otherwise so nothing is lost — and leave free cargo space for the returned kit.",
      "The founding fee is not refunded; you recover the kit and nothing else. After dismantling you're undocked and adrift in the system.",
      "An outpost's built-in fuel bunker can no longer be dismantled on its own — remove it by dismantling the whole outpost."
    ]
  },
